OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FBail has been refused during a special
OL,7,Fcourt sitting which heard in excess of
OL,8,F#1million in cocaine was discovered as
OL,9,Fwell as indecent child imagery and
OL,10,Fattempts to pay for sexual services.
OL,12,FAaron Hudson, 30, from Moorville,
OL,13,FStewartstown is charged with
OL,14,Fpossessing and being concerned in the
OL,15,Fsupply of cocaine and cannabis as well
OL,16,Fas possessing and transferring
OL,17,Fcriminal property.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
