OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777964751
OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FHe is further accused of possessing
OL,7,Fand making indecent images of children
OL,8,Fand attempting to pay for sexual
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,FOffending is alleged to have occurred
OL,12,Fon dates between 20 January and 2 May.
OL,14,FA detective constable from the PSNI
OL,15,FOrganised Crime Branch to a Dungannon
OL,16,FMagistrates Court the cages could be
OL,17,Fconnected.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
