FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777964751
OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FShe explained on 20 January police
OL,7,Fstopped Hudson as he was driving a
OL,8,Fvehicle in the Gosford Road area of
OL,9,FArmagh.
OL,11,FA search recovered two phones and what
OL,12,Fwas considered by police to be a
OL,13,Fledger relating to drug supply and
OL,14,Fcontaining contacts.
OL,16,FHe was not arrested at this time and
OL,17,Fthe phones were sent for examination,
OL,18,Fone of which showed "clear evidence of
OL,19,Finvolvement in the delivery of
OL,20,Fmultiple kilos of drugs" as exchanges
OL,21,Fand collecting cash.
OL,26,@zD@UOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
