OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777964751
OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FCommunication was on various platforms
OL,7,Fincluding Signal and WhatsApp showing
OL,8,Fmessages following up deliveries and
OL,9,Ftransactions.
OL,11,FIt also indicated Hudson was
OL,12,Fcollecting cash on behalf of unknown
OL,13,Fpersons showing names, values and
OL,14,Fexchanges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
