PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777964751
OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FThe second phone was believed to be
OL,7,FHudson's personal device and contained
OL,8,Findecent child imagery comprising 28
OL,9,Fimages and 31 videos in Category A
OL,10,F(the most serious), 19 images and 16
OL,11,Fvideos in Category B and 39 images and
OL,12,F14 videos in Category C.
OL,14,FThere was also contact with sex
OL,15,Fworkers including agreeing prices for
OL,16,Factivity and in one message he said he
OL,17,Fwas obtaining cash and was provided
OL,18,Fwith an address.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
