CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777964751
OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FThis phone also contained some
OL,7,Fevidence of drugs supply and money
OL,8,Flaundering.
OL,10,FOn receipt of this evidence police
OL,11,Farrested Hudson and another device was
OL,12,Fseized which showed a connection to a
OL,13,Fstorage facility in his name.
OL,15,FThis was searched and 11 kilos of
OL,16,Fcocaine were recovered with a street
OL,17,Fvalue of over #1 million which, said
OL,18,Fthe detective, "was a huge find."
OL,26,@zD@POUzD@aO]
