OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FDuring interview Hudson gave an
OL,7,Fexplanation in relation to the sexual
OL,8,Foffending but gave 'no comment'
OL,9,Freplies to the drugs matters.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
