OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777964751
OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FObjecting to bail the detective said,
OL,7,F"The risk of further offending is
OL,8,Fhuge. For the defendant to have
OL,9,Fcontrol of that amount of drugs
OL,10,Findicates he is deeply into this
OL,11,Foffending . This is his lifestyle. He
OL,12,Fhas no legitimate work. This is a loss
OL,13,Fof a huge amount of drugs putting him
OL,14,Fin significant debt which he has no
OL,15,Fmeans of repaying without returning to
OL,16,Fcriminality. There are also concerns
OL,17,Fin terms of sexual offending and there
OL,18,Fis a danger to his own safety once
OL,19,Fthese matters are made known."
OL,26,@oD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
