OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777964751
OL,3,CBail refused after #1m cocaine find in
OL,4,CDungannon and indecent child imagery
OL,6,FDefence solicitor Jarlath Faloon urged
OL,7,Fbail to be granted, telling the court
OL,8,Fwhile Hudson has a record for
OL,9,Fpossessing cannabis 10 years ago there
OL,10,Fis nothing for indecent images.
OL,12,FHe added there will also be enquiries
OL,13,Finto who had access to the storage
OL,14,Ffacility although accepted it was
OL,15,Frented by Hudson.
OL,17,FBut refusing bail District Judge Conor
OL,18,FHeaney said, "The charges are of the
OL,19,Futmost seriousness, not just the drugs
OL,20,Foffending but the sexual matters."
OL,26,@zD@NOU|D@bO]
